Fix overstated reflections data - use claim history instead of PDA offsets 
 
PDA counter offsets (40, 56) include internal recirculation within 
Fee Share V2 program, overstating total fees by 5.6x (80 SOL vs 14 SOL). 
Now derives lifetime totals from verifiable on-chain claim transactions. 
Increased claim history fetch limit from 50 to 100 for accuracy. 
 
